{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896377133,"sessionID":"ses_2845470bcffeOiOnx857OZvVDi","part":{"id":"prt_d7bac36d7001SCCmtPpOUO416r","messageID":"msg_d7bac0ed40018zwpw2dv3UjJK5","sessionID":"ses_2845470bcffeOiOnx857OZvVDi","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-eeb99b453eb74155a307a078be79cec8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sdk-python/tests/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sdk-python/tests/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-040: Python SDK/CLI Tests\n2: \n3: **Module**: sdk-python/tests\n4: **Language**: Python\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Design**: [Stage ST-3 completed]\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Overview\n11: Create comprehensive test coverage for the AgentCube Python SDK and CLI components. Tasks are organized by module and should be completed in the order listed, as some tasks may have dependencies.\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Phase 1: Core SDK Infrastructure Tests\n16: \n17: ### Task 1.1: SDK Test Infrastructure Setup\n18: - [ ] Create test utilities module (`tests/fixtures/`) with common fixtures\n19: - [ ] Configure pytest settings for SDK tests (pytest.ini or pyproject.toml)\n20: - [ ] Set up test coverage configuration (coverage.py)\n21: - [ ] Create conftest.py with shared fixtures for:\n22:   - Mock HTTP clients\n23:   - Mock Kubernetes API clients\n24:   - Temporary directories/workspaces\n25:   - Sample test data\n26: \n27: **Verification**: Run `pytest tests/ -v` with 0 tests passing (infrastructure ready)\n28: \n29: ---\n30: \n31: ### Task 1.2: HTTP Client Tests\n32: - [ ] Create `tests/test_http_client.py`\n33: - [ ] Test HTTP client initialization with default and custom timeouts\n34: - [ ] Test GET requests with query parameters\n35: - [ ] Test POST requests with JSON payload\n36: - [ ] Test PUT requests with JSON payload\